own licenses:

- skills/docx/ — Anthropic's official "docx" skill. © Anthropic, PBC. Governed
  by Anthropic's own terms (see skills/docx/LICENSE.txt), NOT this MIT license.
- skills/humanizer/ — vendored from blader/humanizer (MIT). See
  skills/humanizer/LICENSE.
- library/frameworks/ — the framework index and evidence-labeling standard are
  distilled/adapted from gcamilo/management-consulting (MIT).
